addInitialABMembers(address[]).details: is used to add initital advisory board members

params.abArray: is the list of initial advisory board members

params.tokens: is list of tokens minted for each array element
params.userArray: is list of addresses of members

params._authorized: Authorized member against every role id

authorized(uint256).details: Return member address who holds the right to add/remove any member from specific role.

changeAuthorized(uint256,address).details: Change Member Address who holds the authority to Add/Delete any member from specific role.

params._newAuthorized: New authorized address against role id
params._roleId: roleId to update its Authorized Address

changeDependentContractAddress().details: Iupgradable Interface to update dependent contract address

changeMaxABCount(uint256).details: to change max number of AB members allowed

params._val: is the new value to be set

checkRole(address,uint256).details: Returns true if the given role id is assigned to a member.

params._roleId: Checks member's authenticity with the roleId. i.e. Returns true if this roleId is assigned to member

getMemberLengthForAllRoles().details: Return total number of members assigned against each role id.
getMemberLengthForAllRoles().return: totalMembers Total members in particular role id

isAuthorizedToGovern(address).details: checks if an address is authorized to govern

params._firstAB: is the address of the first AB member
params.memberAuthority: is the authority (role) of the member

members(uint256).details: Gets the member addresses assigned by a specific role
members(uint256).return: roleId Role idallMemberAddress Member addresses of specified role id

payJoiningFee(address).details: Called by user to pay joining membership fee

roles(address).details: Get All role ids array that has been assigned to a member so far.

params._newABAddress: is address of new AB member
params._removeAB: is advisory board member to be removed

switchMembership(address).details: Called by existed member if wish to switch membership to other address.

params._add: address of user to forward membership.

updateRole(address,uint256,bool).details: Assign or Delete a member from specific role.

params._active: active is set to be True if we want to assign this role to member, False otherwise!

withdrawMembership().details: Called by existed member if wish to Withdraw membership.
